             was indicted for <rs id="t17720219-59-off285" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17720219-59-off285" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17720219-59-off285" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing a bank note, value 20 l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17720219-59-victim532" type="victimName">
                           Daniel
                            Bailey
